{"tid":1380604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲將軍澳區巴絲打book定會所","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:41:44.000Z","uid":259154,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1cb98afc9df12a12941b11a9d63e05c2e643bdd3","tid":1380604,"uid":259154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"將軍澳區嘅特色係周街都係私人屋苑，商場，天橋<br />\n一圍堵就困獸鬥，唔知點走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊行嘅終點站 - 單車館附近，有好多私人屋苑<br />\n雖然未知到時會發生咩事<br />\n相信會有好多人去西環<br />\n但我相信亦都會有人留守將軍澳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呼籲大家book 定個會所<br />\n俾大家有個可以避難嘅地方<br />\n住附近嘅居民<br />\n都要凖備好接濟義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4db70570a3dcfcff950d7e35562a8f34912572b","tid":1380604,"uid":283970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72eda74b467d0b6807533ca0f2b054514bfd79a9","tid":1380604,"uid":259154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:48:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"fd05fbbfe27e99eadaa3eef0db0720a69321be37","tid":1380604,"uid":259154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"}]}